    ==============================================
    DASHBOARD PAGE - Ella Rises
    ==============================================
    This is the logged-in user's personal dashboard.
    Shows different content based on user role:
    
    ADMINS see:
    - Total participants count
    - Total donations amount
    - Upcoming events count
    - Quick links to manage pages (participants, events, donations, etc.)
    
    PARTICIPANTS see:
    - Upcoming reservations (events they're signed up for)
    - Milestones completed (achievements earned)
    - Surveys pending (feedback forms to complete)
    - Quick links to their registrations, donations, surveys
    
    Data comes from the /dashboard route in index.js.
    The 'level' variable determines which view to show (admin vs participant).
-->
